/><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72e9f171e3b39b560099cd7da9e820676c074ed","tid":2282942,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"131aab6249a4fd0b017f0b64c532a982a220af28","tid":2282942,"uid":280300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:34:08.000Z","msg":"係咪'叫神走開'或者'對神不敬'咁嘅意思?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:52:23.000Z","msg":"中咗一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa1675e0a4c3cf1617423175264dea4df7feadb","tid":2282942,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:53:09.000Z","msg":"師兄睇完呢本野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wsNpVNj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwsNpVNj.jpg&h=192319e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76f684ddd690608de0557e4bfac2b4acbb1ed1d4","tid":2282942,"uid":64728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:02:05.000Z","msg":"我係中國人呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1825e8f5e403599f92b12124041cc8e52011fd","tid":2282942,"uid":302951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fa1675e0a4c3cf1617423175264dea4df7feadb","tid":2282942,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:53:09.000Z","msg":"師兄睇完呢本野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wsNpVNj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwsNpVNj.jpg&h=192319e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:14:08.000Z","msg":"yup<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本野好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6045f019129fdf6339dfcf4ccf15c3167b53a4","tid":2282942,"uid":302951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:17:52.000Z","msg":"「奉主之名」呢句係誓言，即係結婚誓詞、總統就職誓詞果類，不過呢句更強調神喺誓詞中嘅角色，建基於誠信同對神嘅信服之上。有啲似江湖中人講義氣，好靠自己約束。你無義氣？得，咪比人唾棄囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講返果句先，宗教問題自然由宗教入手。聖經創世記12章開始記載，亞伯拉罕受感召，上帝應許賜佢迦南之地以及子子孫孫。但係以佢75歲高齡<span class=\"x-small\"><del>起唔起到機都成問題</del></span>，天主呢番話似玩鳩佢多，佢走數無人奈得佢何㗎。天主於是叫佢準備幾隻劈開一半嘅動物，佢化身成火從肉塊中經過，並以此為誓。之後仲爭啲叫亞伯拉罕獻埋自己個仔(阿仔無辜㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪搞啦)。<br />\n<br />\n咁大壇嘢背後意思係雖然天主作為真理，唔會違反諾言，但倘若佢食言，佢會照懲罰自己，下場會同啲動物一樣。佢立誓係為咗安撫亞伯拉罕同埋確立之後會做嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n喺聖經到，天主通常以自已或自身一部分借代起誓 : 我指着自己起誓...... / 耶和華指着自己的右手和大能的膀臂起誓...... 呢個成為啲人發誓嘅規則，再加上十誡講明不可妄稱天主之名，即係如果你唔認真亂發誓或者食言就好大罪啦！你等於搵上帝做擔保人然後走數，要佢硬食條爛數，等住比蘇哥燒屎忽啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以喺中世紀，最嚴重嘅粗口係「天主在上」同「以天主(+聖血/聖骨/右手......)發誓」。係呀！呢兩句仲爆過燒山個34字粗口！及後雖然有啟蒙運動、宗教改革等運動削弱宗教權威，但當時(十九世紀頭)仍有一定影響力，以致於個貴族夫人嗌聲Oh God都震驚社會。依家同ABC講兩句佢地就OMG，喺床上仲有Oh Jesus Christ。可見宗教喺近代影響力大減，居然會影響埋啲人對唔同粗口嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd71ee5c6c941f8bf6453365499a4d84914b988","tid":2282942,"uid":25559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:46:08.000Z","msg":"講兩次屌你老母"},{"pid":"e37111fa90607459b55120e2db1863b22b5b8a88","tid":2282942,"uid":363862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T09:25:00.000Z","msg":"半個ling人輕輕一推"},{"pid":"e241f1fd73de9492955f2c6539fcb9da77256051","tid":2282942,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fd71ee5c6c941f8bf6453365499a4d84914b988","tid":2282942,"uid":25559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:46:08.000Z","msg":"講兩次屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T10:04:30.000Z","msg":"有咩慘得過食一舊屎？<br />\n：食兩舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780fc091262f755a145cf801bdf5cf13d1ade5de","tid":2282942,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fd71ee5c6c941f8bf6453365499a4d84914b988","tid":2282942,"uid":25559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:46:08.000Z","msg":"講兩次屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"認真答你<br />\n<br />\n同一句說話講得愈多就愈唔offensive <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}